                        cent.</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>Fǝśśǝḥa Giyorgis is mentioned as the commissioner in the colophon. The
                     Ms. was owned originally by the church Dabra Mikāʾel ʾƎnba Ḥarisay (Mikāʾel ʿAd
                     Ḥǝyaw) (s. the colophon, cp. Additiones 2-3 in MR-033).</provenance>
               </history>
